w1   - 1st order,
w2,q - 2nd order

1/w1 + 1/(q*w2)       = A = (c1*r1*r2 + c3*r1*r3 + c3*r1*r4 + c3*r2*r3 + c3*r2*r4 + c3*r3*r4)/(r1 + r2)
